<section>
<title>Description détaillée</title>

<para><link linkend="_namespace_monolog">Monolog</link> error handler</para>

<para>A facility to enable logging of runtime errors, exceptions and fatal errors.</para>

<para>Quick setup: <computeroutput>ErrorHandler::register($logger);</computeroutput></para>

<para><formalpara><title>Auteur</title>

<para>Jordi Boggiano <link xlink:href="mailto:j.boggiano@seld.be">j.boggiano@seld.be</link> </para>
</formalpara>
</para>
</section>
